-----------
git
-----------

. version control tool
. saves different version of same files
. efficient
. saves memory


-----------
github
-----------

. for collaboration
. can create pull requests
. two types of repositories:
    . public --> anyone can access
    . private --> need to give persmission


-----------
basic commands
-----------

git add 
git commit 
git push 
git pull  --> fetch the latest changes from remote (cloud)

git pull ---> git fetch + git rebase 

git checkout --> to checkout specific branch
